OL,3,CCould the next pope be Ghanaian? Hopes
OL,4,Crise in country as Conclave vote nears
OL,6,FAs the election of a new Pontiff
OL,7,Fnears, could the next head of the
OL,8,FCatholic church be from Ghana? ITV
OL,9,FNews Correspondent Rachel Townsend
OL,10,Freports on the growing excitement in
OL,11,Fthe capital, Accra.
OL,13,FOn almost every street corner in
OL,14,FGhana's capital, Accra, is a
OL,15,Fproclamation of faith.
OL,17,F"To God be the Glory" is one I am
OL,18,Fcurrently looking at from my hotel
OL,19,Froom. In giant font, it covers 15
OL,20,Ffloors of a modern business block.
