OL,3,CCould the next pope be Ghanaian? Hopes
OL,4,Crise in country as Conclave vote nears
OL,6,FCardinal Turkson will join next week's
OL,7,FConclave at the Vatican as a Cardinal.
OL,8,FGiven the secrecy around this
OL,9,Fcenturies-old ritual, whether he comes
OL,10,Fout as a pope is impossible to predict.
OL,12,FBut there is growing excitement in one
OL,13,Fcorner of West Africa that Cardinal
OL,14,FTurkson ` born and raised in a shanty
OL,15,Ftown, the son of a carpenter and
OL,16,Fvegetable seller ` could be the next
OL,17,Fleader of the Catholic church.
