OL,6,FDescribed as a fun, mischievous little
OL,7,Fboy, he cemented his faith during his
OL,8,Fyears at a seminary in the town of
OL,9,FCape Coast.
OL,11,FThe town was the departure point for
OL,12,Fenslaved Africans ` their last sight
OL,13,Fof Africa before leaving for the
OL,14,FAmericas. It is now a bustling fishing
OL,15,Ftown and a place where many remember
OL,16,Ftheir former student, turned scholar,
OL,17,FBishop and then Archbishop.
