OL,6,FThere are currently 262 young men
OL,7,Ftraining to be priests here. They live
OL,8,Fhumble lives; days are spent in deep
OL,9,Ftheological study, but there is a buzz
OL,10,Fhere too. The next pope could have
OL,11,Fwalked these corridors, sat at their
OL,12,Fdesks.
OL,14,F"A black pope, it's huge," Rev Michael
OL,15,FOwusu-Amponsah said.
OL,17,FHe is in his final year at the
OL,18,Fseminary.
